msgctxt "1440"
msgid "Worried Woman"
msgstr "Mujer ansiosa"

msgctxt "1444"
msgid "Akiyama"
msgstr "Akiyama"

msgctxt "1448"
msgid "Talk_No"
msgstr "Talk_No"

msgctxt "1452"
msgid "Talk_Think"
msgstr "Talk_Think"

msgctxt "1456"
msgid "Talk_Yes"
msgstr "Talk_Yes"

msgctxt "84_Worried Woman"
msgid "So this is Sky Finance..."
msgstr "Conque esto es Sky Finance..."

msgctxt "96_Akiyama"
msgid "That's my company. Can I help you with anything?"
msgstr "Esta es mi empresa. ¿Puedo ayudarle?"

msgctxt "108_Worried Woman"
msgid "Oh, uh... Um... It's just, a friend of mine borrowed some money from a loan company that's been pressuring her to pay them back."
msgstr "Ah, no... Es solo que un amigo pidió un préstamo a otra empresa.\n"\n"Dice que es bastante difícil pagar a tiempo."

msgctxt "120_Akiyama"
msgid "I see. Well, it may sound strange coming from me, but people shouldn't borrow money if they can help it."
msgstr "Ah, sí. Como alguien que trabaja en este mundo, mi recomendación\n"\n"es no pedir demasiado dinero prestado."

msgctxt "132_Worried Woman"
msgid "But if your friend's really in a jam, tell her to drop by my office. I may be able to help."
msgstr "Pero si tu amigo se encuentra en serios problemas, pásate por aquí.\n"\n"Quizás pueda ayudar."

msgctxt "144_Worried Woman"
msgid "......"
msgstr "......"

msgctxt "156_Akiyama"
msgid "Tell your friend now, okay?"
msgstr "¿Se lo dirás?"

msgctxt "168_Worried Woman"
msgid "All right... Thank you."
msgstr "Je, sí... Muchas gracias."

